Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra, open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the day I'm going to\Ntake you in for a check up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you that it's\Npointless to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think\NI'm coming here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody called you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You stubborn, narrow-minded woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk, you quack doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been to a doctor\Nsince I was born, but I'm still healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!\NBad news...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Schumann!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fink, the drunkard was hit\Nby a car on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So is he still conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who brought him in\Nis treating him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that some man who happened\Nto be passing by is examining him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You were visiting homes,\Nso that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You let him treat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I tried to stop him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said that he needed to\Napply first aid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because there was a chance that\Nthe patient would choke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?\NHe left without saying his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... he wrote something\Non the medical chart...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"The patient has no money."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"He kept repeating not to\Ntake him to a doctor."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please take this money\Nas his doctor's fee"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an Asian man with a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, what about Fink's treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep him in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... the man only\Napplied first aid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not first aid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,His treatment was complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.82,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}Petra and Schumann
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a problem if you follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go to school.\NYou can't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who\Ncame to my clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and did unnecessary things,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Fink is a broke alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no intention of\Ncharging him for treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably some elite\Nfrom a first-rate hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to show some compassion\Nwhile on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey.\N- Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go, Dieter!\N- Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fink got into a hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fink, the drunkard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... That's a tough task.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Schumann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Fink's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,His life's not in danger. I'm more\Nworried about his alcoholism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,An underclassman from college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's visiting this village\Nduring his vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Chan? Have we met somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He treated Fink for me\Nwhile I was visiting homes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, where do you think I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At Petra's house...\Nyour mother, Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her to come to the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We may need to treat her\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That stubborn woman\Nwon't listen to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act as if it's not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Mom won't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, she raised me this far.\NI don't think she has any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra's life has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was for saving Fink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have died if it wasn't\Nfor your swift treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned so pale\Nwhen you saw the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,at least it's obvious that you're not\Nan elite doctor from a first-rate hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NI don't know how to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Repay me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then help me out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Owowow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your splint is misaligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This may hurt a bit,\Nbut please be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it should be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can probably take it off\Nafter two more weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I made some good cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drink with you all night\Nonce you've healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Progress is good. Five days\Nand you can go back to the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Schone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, take some potatoes.\NThis year's crop is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll come with a truck\Nand take a whole mountain of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NMy specialty is internal medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I do what I can outside my specialty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But things don't go very well\Nwhen I'm by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's nothing here,\Nbut it's a peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're loved by the people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And you really love them too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, huh?\NI lost feelings like that a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come with me\Nto just one more house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are persistent, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll keep coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the same no matter\Nhow many times you come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You quack doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the mother\Nof that police officer earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell sick while farming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to get her to my clinic,\Nbut on the way there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,she said that she's fine\Nand went back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's worrisome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I try to reason with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still loitering there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can loiter wherever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. She'll never come out\Nif you yell like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get you out. I'm not going\Nto lose my reason for living!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I just meant that I wouldn't\Nhave anyone to fight with anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Also, I wouldn't be able to eat\Nher goulash anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up, Mrs. Petra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? A different doctor now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless to talk to\Nthat stubborn woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hate doctors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Well, humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They fiddle around\Nwith peoples' bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and think that they're gods\Nor something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,God, huh? Sometimes I think that\Nit would be great if we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We try our best, but no matter what,\Nwe make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish that I could heal people\Nperfectly like God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always trembling inside\Nwhenever I see my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. At least let me see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell... You're making goulash,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Do you like goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But it seems that Dr. Schumann\Nespecially loves your goulash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's news to me. He always eats it\Nwithout a word whenever I make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...\NMy shoulders are stiff,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looks like\NI have to prepare dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stiff shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Petra, can you put\Nyour chin to your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Owowow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four fingers fit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Some kind of prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably...\Na subarachnoid hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the fax of the arrest warrant\Nfor the murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Make copies of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your mom okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that she collapsed\Nthree days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all right. She wouldn't die\Neven if you killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 72 hours\Nsince the first stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make it.\NWe've got to operate immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if a helicopter\Ncan make it if we call for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,perform the operation\Nif you can... If not... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be my fault again for\Nlosing another person I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure that it's Kenzo Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He might not have gone far!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Set up a barrier along the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be great if we catch him, Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, emergency deployment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I can get a promotion\Nif things go well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heinz, you have a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! This is Heinz...\NOh, hello, Nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom collapsed again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had forced her to\Nget a check up at a national hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,after the first stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one\NI can count on, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought. It's an aneurysm\Nof the middle cerebral artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!\NWe don't have a surgical microscope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or a craniotome here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can try open surgery as long as\NI have an aneurysm clip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too difficult even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She may not live the next time\Nthe cranial aneurysm ruptures...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault that\Nthis happened again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dr. Schumann?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You single-handedly took care of\Nthe patients of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened\Nin the past, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to try our best\Nfor the patient before us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all we can do as doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy, is Dr. Schumann inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's operating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Operating on my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're operating at this clinic\Nrather than taking her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to a hospital in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Tenma is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How's her blood pressure and pulse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure 126/84.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulse 88.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing... He opened her head\Nso fast with just a wire saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have a craniotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we are\Noperating on your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with that gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hands, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of an operation!\NAre you trying to kill your mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is a murder suspect\Nthat's been on the run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed a man in Heidelberg.\NHe's even suspected of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the serial killing of\Nmiddle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that I'd find him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Mom.\NShe saw an opportunity for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, raise your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sterile operating room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bringing in germs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother could die\Nfrom meningitis if you spread it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then quickly stop the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want your mom to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother has\Na subarachnoid hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She first collapsed three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't deal with it now\Nit'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you've got a hostage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're planning to use my mom\Nas a hostage and run away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aneurysm clip and forceps...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aneurysm clip and forceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Petra is your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But what have you done for her\Nin the past five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you visited her even once\Nsince you left the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you ever done\Nfor your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,after she raised you this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, people who are dear to us\Nwill pass away some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the taste of\Nyour mother's goulash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, Petra makes portions\Nfor you out of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I eat what's left over. It's delicious!\NThat taste is superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is desperately fighting\Nto save your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to eat that goulash again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Tenma is here, so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure 140/86. Pulse 82.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Vital signs are stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pionier, you should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, you get some rest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You performed a difficult operation\Nthat lasted three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay alert and watch her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you can propose to Mrs. Petra\Nwhen she gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "propose"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep.\NNot until I take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to propose\Nto my mom, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish! Don't be foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... not someone who can\Npropose to anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was\Nat the university hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I never cared about talking\Nto my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I only thought of how I could\Nraise my position in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I got into the director's faction\Nand wrote papers for the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I even married the director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I pushed forward along\Nthe path of success even after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I never paid any attention to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If I was a real doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have noticed\Nwhen I had seen her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time,\Nmy wife had symptoms
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,which mimicked the common cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have noticed\Nif I were watching closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was liver failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When she took her last breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You finally... paid attention to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to love anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been paying attention\Nto the people of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra was saved because\Nyou were paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still plan on taking\Nthis man away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man who struggled\Nto save your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still think he's a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Heinz. Get me the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I'm sorry. I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The man I saw wasn't Tenma.\NHe was Dr. Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the mistake\Nbecause he was Asian...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor of the national hospital\Nwas sure surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably never thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,he would see such amazing treatment\Nfrom a clinic in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to let\Nthat young doctor go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to make him\Nsomething to eat, but he went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, this village is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Schumann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, you like it here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NThis village may be good for Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only for Dieter. This village\Ncan protect you from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the people here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This village needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay here,\Nyou can save the lives
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of countless people in this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Save countless lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have to kill a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can do\Nsuch a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You try so desperately to save\Npeoples' lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's going no matter\Nwhat you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma won't lose his way\Nif you're with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch Tenma carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:53.57,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}Left Behind
